    "text_1": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "A Game-Changer in Golf & Sportswear",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In a world where sustainability is no longer a choice but a necessity, <strong>Reflo</strong> emerges as a pioneer in performance-wear. Now available at <strong>TRENDYGOLF UK</strong>, this cutting-edge brand is redefining the future of golf & sportswear, combining <strong>premium technical innovation</strong> with an unwavering commitment to <strong>sustainability</strong>.</p><p>Whether it's <strong>golf, padel, training, or running</strong>, Reflo is designed for <strong>athletes at all levels</strong>. But it's not just another sportswear brand; it's a movement that encourages consumers to <strong>\"Move with the People\"</strong> and take a step towards a <strong>more sustainable world</strong>.</p><h2><strong>The Vision: Sustainability Meets Performance</strong></h2><p>Reflo is built on the idea that high-performance sportswear and <strong>eco-conscious living</strong> can go hand in hand. With a <strong>bold mission</strong> to become the <strong>most sustainable sportswear brand in the world</strong>, Reflo does not settle for half measures. Every aspect of its design, production, and logistics is aligned with sustainable practices that push boundaries and set new standards.</p><h3><strong>Active Regeneration™: More Than Just a Buzzword</strong></h3><p>Reflo believes that simply minimising environmental impact isn't enough. Instead, it operates under the philosophy of <strong>Active Regeneration™</strong>, ensuring that every action taken leaves a <strong>positive imprint on the planet</strong>.</p><p>Key highlights of Reflo's <strong>sustainability-driven</strong> approach:</p><ul><li><strong>50% less energy consumption</strong></li><li><strong>70% fewer carbon emissions</strong></li><li><strong>20% less water usage</strong></li><li><strong>Zero oil reliance</strong> (compared with standard polymer production - Source: Repreve)</li><li><strong>Tree planting initiative</strong>: One tree is responsibly planted for every item purchased in collaboration with <strong>Ecologi</strong> and the <strong>Eden Reforestation Project</strong>.</li></ul><p><strong>Circular fashion commitment</strong>: The <strong>Reloop</strong> initiative ensures garments are designed to be fully recyclable at the end of their lifecycle.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
