    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Cutting-Edge Design: Where Style Meets Sustainability",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Reflo is not just about sustainability—it's also about <strong>elite performance and style</strong>. The brand's meticulously crafted sportswear is engineered to move with the body, providing <strong>unparalleled comfort, support, and flexibility</strong> during any activity.</p><h3><strong>Why Athletes Love Reflo</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Breathable, lightweight, and high-performance materials</strong></li><li><strong>Recycled polyester derived from single-use plastic waste</strong></li><li><strong>Intelligent fabric technology</strong> that integrates natural compounds such as <strong>used coffee grounds</strong> to enhance performance features</li><li><strong>Versatile designs</strong> that transition effortlessly between different sports and activities</li></ul><h2><strong>Harry Kane: The Face of Reflo's Sustainability Mission</strong></h2><p>Adding to its credibility and impact, Reflo has partnered with <strong>England's football captain, Harry Kane</strong>, who not only serves as a <strong>brand ambassador</strong> but is also a <strong>lead investor</strong> in Reflo's <strong>£1 million seed funding round</strong>.</p><p>Kane's commitment to <strong>sustainability and high-performance sportswear</strong> aligns seamlessly with Reflo's values. As an avid golfer and athlete, Kane was initially introduced to the brand at <strong>The Icons Series</strong>, where he played alongside sporting legends. After wearing Reflo for over a year, his endorsement and investment solidify his belief in <strong>changing the game for good</strong>.</p><h3><strong>A Commitment Beyond the Game</strong></h3><p>Kane's involvement extends beyond brand endorsement:</p><ul><li><strong>500 trees planted for every goal he scores in the 2023/2024 season</strong></li><li>A push for <strong>sustainable innovation in performancewear</strong></li><li>A vision to merge <strong>elite sports with environmental responsibility</strong></li></ul><p>Kane himself states: <em>\"I'm thrilled to be joining the team here at Reflo. Their dedication to sustainability and performance in golf is inspiring and perfectly aligns with everything I believe in—both on and off the pitch.\"</em></p>"
          }
        }
      },
