    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Sustainability from Production to Packaging",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Eco-Friendly Production & Packaging</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Compostable and biodegradable product packaging</strong> made from glassine paper</li><li><strong>Recycled paper tags & tissue</strong> with hemp string for swing tags</li><li><strong>No single-use plastic</strong> in any part of the packaging</li></ul><h3><strong>Green Logistics & Minimal Waste</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Zero waste to landfill</strong> through <strong>Provenance and Green logistics</strong> partners</li><li><strong>LED bulbs in warehouses</strong>, reducing power consumption by 40% over 10 years</li><li><strong>Paper-free operations</strong> in logistics facilities</li><li><strong>Minimal textile waste</strong> with alternative pattern-cutting techniques</li></ul><h2><strong>Why Reflo is the Future of Performancewear</strong></h2><p>By refusing to cut corners, Reflo is <strong>challenging the norms</strong> of sportswear production. The brand is built on three core pillars:</p><h3><strong>1. Lead with Style</strong></h3><p>Clothing should not only perform well but look good. Reflo ensures its pieces remain at the forefront of both <strong>performance and design</strong>, making them essential wardrobe staples.</p><h3><strong>2. Believe in Less</strong></h3><p>Reflo takes a <strong>minimalist approach to production</strong>, avoiding unnecessary waste, excessive sampling, and overproduction. Instead of chasing trends, they focus on <strong>timeless, high-quality apparel</strong>.</p><h3><strong>3. Innovate for Good</strong></h3><p>Reflo embraces <strong>cutting-edge textile innovations</strong> while acknowledging the challenges in the industry. The brand takes a transparent approach, ensuring that sustainability remains at the heart of its evolution.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
